label: Female
description: Persons whose current gender is female. This includes cisgender and transgender persons who are female.

label: Male
description: Persons whose current gender is male. This includes cisgender and transgender persons who are male.

label: Gender Diverse
description: Persons whose current gender is not exclusively as male or female. It includes people who do not have one gender, have no gender, are non-binary, or are Two-Spirit.

label: Unknown
description: Persons whose gender is not known at the time of data collection. It may or may not get updated at a later point in time. X is different than U.
